Invocation Name: eagle realty
des: Eagle Realty in Myrtle Beach, South Carolina is you source for all real estate needs in the surrounding areas. Our goal is to provide expert service and value adding services to all buyer and seller needing realtor services with homes, condos, land, and commercial properties. We specialize in investment property, second homes, ocean front, retirement, and golf communities. Eagle Realty is ready to work with you wit our team of professional real estate agents in the coastal area of north and south carolina.
